    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "mf_b",
      "x": 72,
      "y": 480,
      "width": 1100,
      "height": 70,
      "text": "Pushed tags:  ghcr.io/<user>/go-viz:latest  \u00b7  ghcr.io/<user>/go-viz:v1.0.0-rc1  (CI computes from git tag).\nEach tag resolves to either amd64 or arm64 layer at pull time based on client platform.  Release workflow: GitHub Actions on tag push \u2192 buildx \u2192 push \u2192 GitHub Release body.",
      "originalText": "Pushed tags:  ghcr.io/<user>/go-viz:latest  \u00b7  ghcr.io/<user>/go-viz:v1.0.0-rc1  (CI computes from git tag).\nEach tag resolves to either amd64 or arm64 layer at pull time based on client platform.  Release workflow: GitHub Actions on tag push \u2192 buildx \u2192 push \u2192 GitHub Release body.",
