      "x": 140,
      "y": 955,
      "width": 420,
      "height": 95,
      "text": "/tmp/go-viz/sources/<id>/       unpacked user ZIP\n/tmp/go-viz-cache/<id>/         parsed.gob, graph.json, dead-code.json\nTTL sweeper goroutine removes entries older than 30 min idle.\nOptionally: -v host_cache:/tmp/go-viz-cache to persist across restarts.",
