      "x": 690,
      "y": 720,
      "width": 440,
      "height": 200,
      "text": "Chrome / Firefox / Safari\n\u2192 GET  http://localhost:8080/              (SPA shell from embed.FS)\n\u2192 POST http://localhost:8080/api/projects   (multipart ZIP)\n\u2192 EventSource(\"/api/projects/{id}/analyze\")  (SSE)\n\u2192 GET  http://localhost:8080/api/projects/{id}/graph\nlocalStorage:  last project_id, UI prefs (theme, filters)",
      "originalText": "Chrome / Firefox / Safari\n\u2192 GET  http://localhost:8080/              (SPA shell from embed.FS)\n\u2192 POST http://localhost:8080/api/projects   (multipart ZIP)\n\u2192 EventSource(\"/api/projects/{id}/analyze\")  (SSE)\n\u2192 GET  http://localhost:8080/api/projects/{id}/graph\nlocalStorage:  last project_id, UI prefs (theme, filters)",
